plyTime":"2016-12-15T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>gogo7188某幾首歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n浮舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6a21ByYAWNQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6a21ByYAWNQ&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=459b5d87\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6a21ByYAWNQ</a>"},{"pid":"99d419fe8009d30bd4408fc1c928e26489934638","tid":40972,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>gogo7188某幾首歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n浮舟<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6a21ByYAWNQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6a21ByYAWNQ&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=459b5d87\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6a21ByYAWNQ</a></blockquote><br />\n呢個好似純搖滾...只是唱日文。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我講緊既和風多數都係用大量漢字，著華麗和服，或者多用三味線、尺八、箏呢類唐代日本樂器。<br />\n<br />\n例如好似陰陽座<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v86m2RdPSo8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv86m2RdPSo8&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=119ff821\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v86m2RdPSo8</a>"},{"pid":"612c64d889d5953a5040c2ad7a15e689910dff64","tid":40972,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過<br />\n有冇多啲磚<br />\n一陣Down落嚟慢慢研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千本桜本來好似係類似動漫歌的東西（一開始得初音版本），入面講好多日本歷史野，詳情可以GOOGLE下。（例如講維新改革日本舊社會之類）。<br />\n<br />\n六兆年と一夜物語、千本桜、暁ノ糸呢三首我暫時覺得最好Ｊ。"},{"pid":"02a9ece2c37da0c5408a7a3c9f0c8bdbd60b2d6a","tid":40972,"uid":57839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78484d24f1649ad16c350b179584d3c7a361fc1b","tid":40972,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"我推介和楽器バンド 原因，係覺得日本人真係好犀利，將一Ｄ沒落傳統樂器（起碼好少後生仔會喜歡）再用搖滾樂包裝，配合埋日本自己獨有圖騰（例如劍扇舞、天狗、和服），再向西方輸出。<br />\n<br />\n佢地好似係美國已經開過幾場演唱會，有時候我覺得，點解中國樂器點解唔用呢種方法再行銷（女子十二樂坊真係好老土）。"},{"pid":"c6dc96d3744ff5b1af43764db12397a09ea18c35","tid":40972,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nゆう子，こんばんは"},{"pid":"ec5e377340e020e61131857f7fb5428bf208e826","tid":40972,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過<br />\n有冇多啲磚<br />\n一陣Down落嚟慢慢研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千本桜本來好似係類似動漫歌的東西（一開始得初音版本），入面講好多日本歷史野，詳情可以GOOGLE下。（例如講維新改革日本舊社會之類）。<br />\n<br />\n六兆年と一夜物語、千本桜、暁ノ糸呢三首我暫時覺得最好Ｊ。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歷史jj<br />\n幾熟明治<br />\n一陣google中文歌詞再聽<br />\n<br />\nOk"},{"pid":"61eadf276a08b6105ecb892814b80f2aabd91cb4","tid":40972,"uid":61154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未聽過<br />\n有冇多啲磚<br />\n一陣Down落嚟慢慢研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千本桜本來好似係類似動漫歌的東西（一開始得初音版本），入面講好多日本歷史野，詳情可以GOOGLE下。（例如講維新改革日本舊社會之類）。<br />\n<br />\n六兆年と一夜物語、千本桜、暁ノ糸呢三首我暫時覺得最好Ｊ。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歷史jj<br />\n幾熟明治<br />\n一陣google中文歌詞再聽<br />\n<br />\nOk</blockquote><br />\n